	        <table border="1" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerTitleCompanyLabel">Chief Executive Officer, Spark Unlimited (Call of Duty: Finest Hour)</span></td>
		        </tr>
		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerBioLabel">Craig Allen is the Chief Executive Officer and a co-founder of Spark Unlimited™, a company dedicated to creating artistically driven, high-quality video game franchises. CALL OF DUTY™: FINEST HOUR™, the first game developed by Spark Unlimited™, was published by Activision® and released in November 2004. Mr. Allen brings to Spark Unlimited™ over ten years of industry experience in managing creative production, launching new consumer brands and generating global business opportunities as they become enabled through new technology. Formally the Executive Vice President and General Manager of Jim Henson Interactive, Mr. Allen was the primary creative architect behind The Jim Henson Company's expanded digital media activities from 1998-2002. In this position, Mr. Allen worked to bring a wide variety of companies together (from traditional media groups to emerging and new media concerns) in order to create new products and business ventures that yielded a portfolio of video games, online entertainment, wireless gaming, and enhanced consumer products.</span></td>
